to use ShinyLive in the browser is that it's all done through JavaScript. And what that means is

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:28.000
you get all the benefits and all of the security benefits of JavaScript, but the security benefits

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:32.639
sometimes constrain you, because JavaScript doesn't want you just executing anything or

